Each image is carefully planned and selected by us to maintain the highest standards both creatively and commercially. Our creative team monitors present and future trends to develop image concepts around current topics.

publicInformation.bio: The Hero collection is best-in-class, known for driving diversity and relevant imagery, pushing the boundaries of what is expected from stock.
publicInformation.longBio:
We’re image obsessed.
From day one our story has been about our passion to create great images. We eat, sleep, and breathe the details—constantly evolving ways to make more unique, relevant, and engaging imagery.

Canadian made, we started Hero in 2012 after a decade building the industry’s top performing global stock photography brands. It was a risky time for a group of makers to strike out on our own, but we knew our deep understanding of the power of images and their impact on brand identity gave us something unique to offer the marketing world. Today, images from our collection represent top brands around the globe.

publicInformation.bio: Professional team with a passion for making Cinematic Stock content, using top equipment: RED 8K Monstro cinema camera and Zeiss Supreme Lenses.
publicInformation.longBio:
Gorodenkoff Productions is a world-leading creator of high-quality Stock Footage content. Our company is based in Estonia, small European country that’s renowned for its love for technology and all things digital, so are we.

We gathered a team of like-minded professionals, people with inexhaustible imagination and desire to create new stories, situations, and narratives that can be used by our dear customers all over the world.

Sometimes we think that the real world is not enough, so we build our own sets, so we can shoot familiar surroundings but look at them from a different, more interesting angle. We use only high-end cinematic equipment (like RED DSCM2 8K Helium, Zeiss Supreme lenses, and ARRI Lights) that gives us the best video quality and cinematic light.
